^ "U.S. Geothermal Provides Company Update". The Wall Street Journal. January 13, 2014. Retrieved February 25, 2014. 
^ "US Geothermal Inc: NYSEMKT:HTM quotes & news". Google Finance. 2015. Retrieved November 17, 2015. 



